  <summary>The orb ponderer's arena first-person shooter</summary>
  
  <url type="homepage">https://covacha.net.ar/~ramiro/public_git/spelloff</url>
  <url type="help">https://covacha.net.ar/~ramiro/public_git/spelloff</url>
  <url type="contact">https://covacha.net.ar/~ramiro/</url>
  <url type="donation">https://ramirobasile.itch.io/spelloff</url>
  <url type="vcs-browser">https://covacha.net.ar/~ramiro/public_git/spelloff</url>
  
  <description>
	  <p><em>This game is an early prototype.</em></p>
	  <p>
	    Spelloff is a multiplayer first-person shooter game. It plays like traditional arena-shooters such as Quake. It features fast-paced 1 vs. 1 duels and configurable free and team deathmatch modes.
    </p>
  </description>
  
